{"tid":205692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【終結者嚟喇】Terminator成真！？　戰鬥民族搶先開第一槍","createTime":"2017-04-18T03:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T05:59:33.000Z","uid":20738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f27dd1117efe5a6aef3c241fe805ff5f2137af","tid":205692,"uid":20738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:19:32.000Z","msg":"【終結者嚟喇】Terminator成真！？　戰鬥民族搶先開第一槍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/tech/art/20170418/19992943\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ftech%2Fart%2F20170418%2F19992943&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19tr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=e4f9867e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ftech%2Fart%2F20170418%2F19992943&h=506fe03f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/tech/art/20170418/19992943</a><br />\n<br />\n相信好多人同肥通一樣，細細個開始就飲荷李活電影奶水大！我一直認為Terminator（終結者）係美國嘅產物，不過最近睇完網上一條片，我的世界被顛覆了！<br />\n<br />\n佢個名叫FEDOR！設計是非常類人的機械人；不過並唔係由美國出品，反而是出自戰鬥民族－－俄羅斯設計師所開發；其實早在2014年已經開始了呢項計劃，據知以往的戰績，係用兩隻腳行走時，就算突然遇上重擊，佢都識得自己平衡；精細的操作，例如開門鎖、燒焊、揸車，佢都完全做到！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n看FEDOR的關節位，活動能力相當高。<br />\n <br />\n與真人作槍擊比賽，由於FEDOR沒有調節呼吸的問題，瞄準及開槍的確要比真人為快。<br />\n不過最近終於露出佢嘅本性，就係試槍擊！是否百發百中真係唔敢講，不過片中看見它手執雙槍，標靶一個一個的被射下來，感覺真係相當令人毛骨悚然！何解？機械人真的可以做出如真人般的判斷，知道何時應該開槍嗎？老實講！直到今天，不少手執真槍的「人」，還是不斷地重複犯着同樣的錯誤；如果只係想測試FEDOR對操控工具的精確度，又可否不要找這樣的殺器，放在它們的手上？<br />\n<br />\n不過點都好啦，FEDOR預計2021年可以成功投產；故事的發展，係FEDOR會揸車去你屋企，幫你整返好反鎖的門，及燒焊壞了的傢俱；還是如Terminator般揸車到你屋企樓下，然後開門入屋&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2psFFFp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2psFFFp&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19tr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=8930be71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2psFFFp</a>"},{"pid":"d6b0aea14408dfed21c3a0e8f1bdc4cec38ea3b7","tid":205692,"uid":46140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:25:09.000Z","msg":"bastion play of the game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6888b27da99f9af7057605447a17c93957ae1046","tid":205692,"uid":7776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:48:44.000Z","msg":"有埋skyline就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1ac3ea76da78eace9cf7d5956b023ad029d34e","tid":205692,"uid":71441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:52:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>bastion play of the game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nomnic crisis <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc25d3b18730d8a3a80808a40fe6bbe4838aa25b","tid":205692,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:52:44.000Z","msg":"mola mola"},{"pid":"c59f105313c08e7355f88566bccf4b18b5ad4be1","tid":205692,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有埋skyline就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我要揸GTR"},{"pid":"ec6031034215e3aca6a74b5c97c334ca26bcd312","tid":205692,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T04:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nFEDOR is skynet<br />\nskynet is FEDOR"},{"pid":"da4c8227fef1be8662fedced4e821f0cbe45e6ad","tid":205692,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T04:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2016/12/fedor.png?w=748&amp;h=413&amp;crop=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmetrouk2.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F12%2Ffedor.png%3Fw%3D748%26h%3D413%26crop%3D1&h=62e4c576&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b2abecd7c74c1659e0b63d0d5ce628674437280","tid":205692,"uid":7703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-